title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlights/maps
description: Description: An exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table containing highlights/maps, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService's getMetaData() function.
EB: The data from the table should be exported successfully without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the attached report.
2. Export the data from a table containing highlights/maps.
3. Observe the exception being thrown in the ReportEngineService's getMetaData() function.
